| sex  | COUNT(*) |
+------+----------+
| NULL |        1 |
| f    |        4 |
| m    |        4 |
+------+----------+
@end example

(In this output, @code{NULL} indicates ``sex unknown.'')

Number of animals per combination of species and sex:

@example
mysql> SELECT species, sex, COUNT(*) FROM pet GROUP BY species, sex;
