is now a reserved word. :(
@item
Add support for @code{INSERT INTO table ... VALUES(...),(...),(...)},
to allow inserting multiple rows with a single statement.
@item
@code{INSERT INTO tbl_name} is now also cached when used with @code{LOCK TABLES}.
